description:
Misora Remi is a clumsy, often scatter-brained, woman who took over as a teaching assistant at Kaimei High School when Sayama went on maternity leave. She was formerly a host of the educational childrens` show Can Mommy Come Too? and tends to refer to herself as "oneesan." She is currently engaged to Chuu-san.
Source: Sket Dance Wikia
name: Misora Remi
